name: Hello World!
tagline: Testing out GitHub's free web hosting
body:
### Hello World!
This is a little test.

### Free and Easy
This template was created automatically through GitHub and I modified the simple markdown to create the content. Easy peasey.

### Live Source
You can submit pull requests to this live site. You'll see those changes immediately after I accept the merge. Pretty cool.

Here's the [GitHub Project](https://github.com/partialinfinity/partialinfinity.github.io)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
